<i>adverb</i>: 엄히 [엄히], 엄중히 [엄중히], 엄정히 [엄정히], 엄밀히 [엄밀히], 엄격히 [엄껴키] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>adverb</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>엄히 [엄히]</dt><br>
<dd>1. severely; rigorously</dd><br>
<dd>규칙을 적용하거나 예절을 가르치는 일 등이 매우 철저하고 바르게.</dd><br>
<dd>In a very thorough and right manner in applying a rule or teaching etiquette.</dd><br>
<dd>2. rigorously; strictly</dd><br>
<dd>일이나 행동이 잘못되지 않도록 주의가 철저하게.</dd><br>
<dd>In a thoroughly careful manner so that something does not go wrong or one does not behave wrongly.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>엄중히 [엄중히]</dt><br>
<dd>1. strictly; stringently; sternly</dd><br>
<dd>매우 엄하게.</dd><br>
<dd>In a very strict manner.</dd><br>
<dd>2. strictly</dd><br>
<dd>엄격하고 정중하게.</dd><br>
<dd>Sternly and politely.</dd><br>
<dd>3. severely</dd><br>
<dd>그냥 넘길 수 없을 정도로 중대하게.</dd><br>
<dd>So seriously as to be hard to overlook.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>엄정히 [엄정히]</dt><br>
<dd>1. strictly; rigidly</dd><br>
<dd>엄격하고 바르게.</dd><br>
<dd>In a strict and right manner.</dd><br>
<dd>2. fairly; impartially</dd><br>
<dd>날카롭고 공정하게.</dd><br>
<dd>In a sharp and fair manner.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>엄밀히 [엄밀히]</dt><br>
<dd>strictly; precisely</dd><br>
<dd>빈틈이나 잘못이 전혀 없을 만큼 엄격하고 세밀하게.</dd><br>
<dd>In a manner of being strict and minute without any loopholes or errors.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>엄격히 [엄껴키]</dt><br>
<dd>strictly; sternly; rigorously</dd><br>
<dd>말, 태도, 규칙 등이 매우 엄하고 철저하게.</dd><br>
<dd>In a manner of being very strict and thorough in one's speech, attitude, rules, etc.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>